### Release an active lease (graceful shutdown of the backend process).
DELETE http://localhost:7878/api/v1/backends/leases/rl_7c4b2d10 HTTP/1.1
X-Extension-Id: local-llm

### Response 204
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content

### Response 403 — lease owned by a different extension
HTTP/1.1 403 Forbidden
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "LEASE_NOT_OWNED",
    "category": "auth",
    "message": "Lease rl_7c4b2d10 is owned by extension 'other-extension', not 'local-llm'"
  }
}
